snippet.title: The Empty Turnabout [FT] Part 1: Is This A Locked Room?
snippet.description:
[A Visual Novelty]

We're playing a DWaM game, it probably is. We'll see how well this goes for Apollo in court here. Apollo returns to the courtroom after an undisclosed absence for an undisclosed reason to take a case on very very short notice. How well could this possibly go?

We'll find out.

-------------------------------
Game made by DWaM on Ace Attorney Online!

Play it here: http://www.aaonline.fr/forum/viewtopic.php?f=15&t=9978
DWaM on Twitter: https://twitter.com/DWaM22
DWaM's non-fancase content (Short stories, novellas, and other games) can be found here: 
https://dwams-mysteries.carrd.co/
